title: mondaysRmurder EP 2: The Yogurt Shop Murders
author: MaryGirl Moody
comment: Im so excited to catch up on all of these episodes. Love you Mary
Mary I am enjoying this series, keep them coming!

Very well done.
real cases like this creep me out more than fiction depictions.

Any Austin folks wanna form a group and meet up for weekly talk and coffee?  I'm still upset the murderers haven't been caught.  Maybe the police know more than we think, and decided to let the case go cold.
description: On December 6th, 1991, four young teenage girls were horribly murdered in a neighborhood yogurt shop. 26 years later, the case is still unsolved.
